export const filelist = [
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1001.697_1007.38.mp3`, "text": `A little bit of... I lost some compression in my vertebra.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1009.04_1013.802.mp3`, "text": `Maybe there's just some general crumbling of the bone throughout my body.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1014.303_1016.043.mp3`, "text": `But an inch, I mean, that's considerable.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1016.063_1028.719.mp3`, "text": `Especially for someone who... So, you know, I think about myself as a big person, not necessarily a tall one, but just sort of big, a big person.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1030.359_1034.303.mp3`, "text": `Yeah, I just, I fill up the allotted space for a person.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1049.895_1068.306.mp3`, "text": `Yeah, it feels like there's a, well, for instance, on a tour bus, if you ever are in a situation where you're in a band and you're touring on a bus, the bunks in a tour bus are made for a generally sized person.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1069.286_1075.47.mp3`, "text": `Because tour buses have to accommodate musicians of all kinds and hockey players and whoever else.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1076.814_1083.189.mp3`, "text": `But when I climb into a bunk on a tour bus, I fill up the entire area.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1084.669_1091.271.mp3`, "text": `And it's very uncomfortable for me because it's uncomfortable for everybody to travel on a tour bus.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1091.931_1103.475.mp3`, "text": `But there is no room for me to even crack my knuckles because in order to do that, I have to spill out of the bunk.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1110.055_1110.335.mp3`, "text": `I do.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1110.455_1138.51.mp3`, "text": `I do like, I mean, the thing is I'm not grotesquely large, but, but, um, I mean, certainly when I get onto it, when I get onto a normal airplane and I don't want to make this an airplane podcast, but when I get onto an airplane, it does feel like everything, like I am being gaslighted a little bit and everything has been shrunk by, by, by, by, by, by, by, by, by, by, by, by, by, by, by, by, by, And I sit down and it's just like, can this seriously be the amount of room allocated to a person?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1147.094_1156.099.mp3`, "text": `Well, I'm hyper-conscious of other people's space because I'm an introverted person and an INFJ or whatever.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1156.719_1160.041.mp3`, "text": `And so I do not want to elbow into someone else's space.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1160.501_1169.047.mp3`, "text": `Certainly, if I sit next to another big guy and he starts to try and take over the armrest... This will not stand.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1169.728_1171.21.mp3`, "text": `I will battle him.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1171.931_1179.823.mp3`, "text": `I will battle him for a twelve hour flight for occupation of one half of my allotted one half of that armrest.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1179.923_1180.203.mp3`, "text": `Yeah.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1181.585_1186.641.mp3`, "text": `But I'm not going to crowd into somebody else's armrest area.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1194.667_1195.127.mp3`, "text": `Oh, I know.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1195.167_1196.568.mp3`, "text": `You're just swimming in it over there.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1211.421_1219.148.mp3`, "text": `I have a friend that I've done quite a bit of traveling with who is also a very big guy, and he does have that sort of sensibility.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1220.049_1223.792.mp3`, "text": `Because he's big, he's entitled to more space.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1223.852_1224.773.mp3`, "text": `He does need it.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1225.952_1228.673.mp3`, "text": `but there's a difference between needing it and being entitled to it.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1229.394_1234.036.mp3`, "text": `And so when the person in front of him leans the seat back, he's in, he's in there.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1234.636_1236.717.mp3`, "text": `He gets furious about it.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1236.878_1239.299.mp3`, "text": `He, but he's also a passive aggressive person.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1239.339_1245.722.mp3`, "text": `So he, he, he doesn't tap the guy on the shoulder and say, excuse me, sir, can you not do that?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1246.202_1255.067.mp3`, "text": `He just kind of like every time he shifts around in his seat, he makes sure to knee the, the person in front of him in the back, you know, uh, as hard as he can.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1255.838_1259.28.mp3`, "text": `But I feel like you have paid the same amount of money for your seat as I have.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1259.36_1263.963.mp3`, "text": `So you are entitled to use that space however you like.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1264.323_1276.029.mp3`, "text": `If you want to set up a bunch of little Hummel figurines along your side of the armrest and talk to them and play with them throughout the course of the flight.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1276.069_1282.513.mp3`, "text": `while I am, you know, like I go into flying, I go into it fully aware.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1282.613_1283.334.mp3`, "text": `I know how it is.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1285.207_1290.209.mp3`, "text": `So I can't blame you, my seatmate for this, for this problem.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1290.789_1294.731.mp3`, "text": `And in fact, as we know, you can blame no one except global capitalism.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1295.311_1296.852.mp3`, "text": `It's the only thing you can be mad at.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1297.172_1311.001.mp3`, "text": `And the only way you can express anger at global capitalism is to tweet about it the most ineffectual way, either that or to go to Bernie Sanders, uh, rallies and wave a hand-painted sign.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_13.23_15.391.mp3`, "text": `Oh, things are looking up.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1311.881_1312.781.mp3`, "text": `Those are your options.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1326.544_1327.804.mp3`, "text": `Absolutely.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1328.244_1335.087.mp3`, "text": `I mean, if you saw what I eat you would be walk me through it.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1348.951_1359.795.mp3`, "text": `Uh, so I do not have very many rituals in the sense of, uh, that I do the same thing every time, but I am forty six years old, almost forty seven years old.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1361.659_1370.821.mp3`, "text": `And I have persisted in eating pretty much any and everything I want.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1372.805_1378.208.mp3`, "text": `Well, well past the point that I should have taken some charge over my diet.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1378.728_1378.949.mp3`, "text": `Right.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1379.309_1381.63.mp3`, "text": `I did a couple of years ago stop eating gluten.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_138.777_139.878.mp3`, "text": `I would love to see the.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1394.458_1395.858.mp3`, "text": `Yeah, it makes me feel bad.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1395.878_1401.682.mp3`, "text": `And so now I am eating gluten, although I recognize that it's bad for me and it makes me feel bad.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1401.702_1402.202.mp3`, "text": `Okay.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1402.934_1413.917.mp3`, "text": `But I'm always trying to moderate to manage my psychological space or the many halls of my psychological Versailles.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_141.422_146.343.mp3`, "text": `I'm picturing that it's kind of a shoulder-mounted, like, sorry.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1414.857_1422.259.mp3`, "text": `I'm constantly trying to move the furniture around in these big mirrored rooms to make them seem more livable.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1423.419_1426.98.mp3`, "text": `And so part of that is food.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1428.18_1436.5.mp3`, "text": `But I absolutely should have a long time ago needed to start watching what I eat because it's just one of those things that happens to people.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1437.121_1447.046.mp3`, "text": `It's a normal person thing that at a certain point you can't just keep eating huge banquets at one o'clock in the morning without suffering enormous consequences.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1447.146_1454.089.mp3`, "text": `But I have a, but I have a kind of physicality and a constitution that allows it, I guess.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1454.65_1460.57.mp3`, "text": `I mean, it's hard to measure, but, because I've never really gotten a handle on it.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1461.19_1465.953.mp3`, "text": `But I still take great solace in food.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_147.663_149.704.mp3`, "text": `Like a sorry measurer.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1470.016_1476.901.mp3`, "text": `And I do not eat... The USDA food pyramid.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1476.921_1495.444.mp3`, "text": `If you took that food pyramid and you turned it upside down, and then you cut the bottom off of it so that it could stand instead of balance on a point... That would be, that'd be, yeah, that, that would kind of be how, how I've always approached food.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_149.724_150.424.mp3`, "text": `Yeah.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_150.724_155.505.mp3`, "text": `Sort of like a Ghostbusters backpack or something that the study participants were wearing.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1523.691_1529.454.mp3`, "text": `I definitely want people to think that I'm a heavy dude in the sort of – in the super fly sense.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1530.234_1533.516.mp3`, "text": `Because I am definitely a heavy dude in that sense.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1535.036_1537.197.mp3`, "text": `But no, that's the thing.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1537.277_1545.596.mp3`, "text": `I mean there are lots of people like me who can absorb – who can absorb – sort of the nutrient content.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1545.676_1547.198.mp3`, "text": `i mean i'm like a blue whale.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1547.218_1559.568.mp3`, "text": `i i've taken so much nutrition uh and the form of like the krill of ten thousand donuts or whatever.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_155.925_161.427.mp3`, "text": `And every time they said, I'm sorry, it made a kind of grinding sound.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1559.588_1562.23.mp3`, "text": `uh and it's just not it's.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1563.21_1564.131.mp3`, "text": `it's not clear.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1564.672_1565.252.mp3`, "text": `you know what it is.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1565.272_1566.333.mp3`, "text": `i just have a density.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1566.933_1567.314.mp3`, "text": `i have an.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1567.494_1568.775.mp3`, "text": `i have an extraordinary density.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1570.738_1579.36.mp3`, "text": `A little bit, just a little teeny piece of me has the gravity of many planets.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1579.66_1580.06.mp3`, "text": `Right.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1582.741_1582.921.mp3`, "text": `Yeah.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1599.132_1601.213.mp3`, "text": `Just a few percentage, maybe ten percent.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1601.353_1601.833.mp3`, "text": `Yeah.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1601.974_1602.714.mp3`, "text": `This is the thing, though.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1602.754_1610.438.mp3`, "text": `I mean, if you... This is because God is hilarious and full of pranks.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1611.519_1618.983.mp3`, "text": `And so, if you take a picture of Dan Benjamin, you look like you are a perfectly normal person.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1620.364_1625.386.mp3`, "text": `And then... No, and the thing is, you can go into stores and buy things that fit you.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1625.406_1629.412.mp3`, "text": `You can get into... You sit down in a chair and you say, what a comfortable chair.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1629.832_1635.703.mp3`, "text": `You go through doorways and feel like there's plenty of space in this doorway for me to go through it carrying a bag.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1635.723_1640.511.mp3`, "text": `And the thing is, I have friends that are a lot bigger than me.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_164.087_166.848.mp3`, "text": `But there was a Canadian aspect to this study?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1641.432_1650.915.mp3`, "text": `That I can only imagine, even if they pay the premium to sit in the big seats, it's not enough.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1658.677_1664.339.mp3`, "text": `I mean, one of the things about being a traveling entertainer is that you do meet a lot of people.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_166.908_167.128.mp3`, "text": `Is that?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1665.48_1672.545.mp3`, "text": `And... And in the course of that meeting a lot of people, some of them become your friends, a great many of them actually.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1672.565_1683.275.mp3`, "text": `I mean, statistically, proportionately, I probably have as many friends as a normal person, but I know so many more people that I end up having a lot more friends.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1685.002_1688.384.mp3`, "text": `And some of those friends end up being huge.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1689.104_1690.865.mp3`, "text": `They are large people.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1691.065_1693.867.mp3`, "text": `I also know a lot of really, really, really tiny people.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1694.407_1704.692.mp3`, "text": `People all across the wide spectrum, which is how I can conclude that God is pranking us all the time.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_17.471_18.112.mp3`, "text": `Oh, well, no.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1707.414_1725.786.mp3`, "text": `Because the variation... exceeds like what is necessary and goes over into the, into the realm of like the, this is impossible that this little very small person and this very large person are the same species.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_171.197_171.477.mp3`, "text": `I see.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_171.517_174.139.mp3`, "text": `Yeah, they do say they're sorry.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1725.806_1731.672.mp3`, "text": `It's, it's, it's excessive and into the realm of comedy.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1731.692_1731.792.mp3`, "text": `Yeah.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_174.499_175.479.mp3`, "text": `They do say that a lot.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1743.754_1747.097.mp3`, "text": `Well, I had a finger in a cast, which is another hilarious.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1748.137_1749.598.mp3`, "text": `That's quite a hilarious accessory.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1749.698_1750.019.mp3`, "text": `Yeah.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_175.499_179.602.mp3`, "text": `That's one of their signature moves.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1750.739_1750.879.mp3`, "text": `Yep.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1774.523_1778.786.mp3`, "text": `yeah right and you know and i was surprised that that didn't catch on.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1779.226_1784.209.mp3`, "text": `i'm surprised look more people didn't start splinting their index finger.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1784.229_1788.631.mp3`, "text": `and because it really it's very emphatic did it heal.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1790.13_1791.732.mp3`, "text": `Hell no, frankly.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1793.753_1794.334.mp3`, "text": `Oh, it works.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1794.474_1794.914.mp3`, "text": `It works.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1794.974_1803.742.mp3`, "text": `It's just, it's been a year since I broke my finger and it still is stiff and I favor it.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_18.452_19.392.mp3`, "text": `Actually, not at all.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1803.762_1815.633.mp3`, "text": `I have a good friend who is a flat track motorcycle racer and he broke his leg pretty severely.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1817.039_1820.221.mp3`, "text": `earlier this year and he's same age as I am.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_182.715_184.796.mp3`, "text": `so people in advance can you read them to me?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1821.582_1822.862.mp3`, "text": `And I said, you know, how's the leg?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1822.882_1823.463.mp3`, "text": `Is it healing up?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1823.523_1825.984.mp3`, "text": `And he was like, not really.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1826.965_1840.793.mp3`, "text": `And in, in his sort of resigned tone, I heard, I heard the first awareness of mortality that I'd ever heard from this guy.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1841.828_1842.769.mp3`, "text": `he's one of these people.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1842.809_1850.232.mp3`, "text": `that was all, he was going to live forever and he was always going to be young and, and he was going to be jumping motorcycles at sixty-five.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1850.292_1850.653.mp3`, "text": `Right.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1850.793_1851.813.mp3`, "text": `McQueen, never die.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1851.833_1855.615.mp3`, "text": `And, and in this like, not really.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1855.755_1865.28.mp3`, "text": `What, what he, what we both understood was that he had broken a limb past the point where healing was something you could count on.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1866.841_1868.201.mp3`, "text": `And now he was healing.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1868.842_1869.222.mp3`, "text": `Sure.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1869.602_1870.903.mp3`, "text": `More or less, he was healing.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1871.809_1873.19.mp3`, "text": `But he was never going to be the same.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1874.67_1875.31.mp3`, "text": `It was terrible.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1875.931_1884.094.mp3`, "text": `And this broken finger was the first real... I mean, I've sustained some injuries that I never recovered from.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1885.174_1902.601.mp3`, "text": `But the failure to recover was... I could attribute some aspect of it to the fact that I didn't rehabilitate myself properly or I injured myself, re-injured myself properly.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_19.472_25.074.mp3`, "text": `But it's considered polite in our culture to always have something positive to say.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1904.974_1907.575.mp3`, "text": `On top of an older injury.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1907.655_1913.438.mp3`, "text": `I mean, there were a lot of reasons why I didn't come all the way back from some earlier slights.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1914.219_1918.401.mp3`, "text": `But this one was one where I was diligent about rehabilitating.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1918.621_1932.208.mp3`, "text": `And ultimately, I'm just past the... I have macular degeneration and I can no longer... I can no longer drink coffee at eleven p.m.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1933.048_1937.151.mp3`, "text": `And I have to monitor the amount of sriracha I put on things.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1937.911_1941.714.mp3`, "text": `And now I broke my finger and it's always going to be a little stiff.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1942.555_1943.775.mp3`, "text": `It's just like, come on.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1943.795_1944.976.mp3`, "text": `This is bullshit.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1945.416_1951.881.mp3`, "text": `In my mind, I am only just beginning what I imagine is the start of a thousand year reich.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1954.219_1974.736.mp3`, "text": `yeah but in my body i am already showing innumerable signs of irrevocable decay and that's just so annoying and feels like and not only is it annoying but so commonplace it's so regular and normal.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1974.916_1979.52.mp3`, "text": `yep that that too is is boggling.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1980.993_1981.754.mp3`, "text": `How do we do it?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1981.914_1984.255.mp3`, "text": `How do we humans manage this?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_1984.716_1986.097.mp3`, "text": `Not very well, I think.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2009.997_2011.14.mp3`, "text": `Are you cautious, Dan?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2020.036_2022.577.mp3`, "text": `person you're averagely cautious.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2049.612_2051.635.mp3`, "text": `Would you catch a baseball open-handed?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2052.636_2053.556.mp3`, "text": `Who threw it?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2054.536_2057.639.mp3`, "text": `If somebody hit a foul ball and you were sitting in the stands at a baseball game.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2057.659_2058.9.mp3`, "text": `Oh, yeah, absolutely, yes.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2058.92_2060.282.mp3`, "text": `Put your hand out and catch it.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2065.426_2072.768.mp3`, "text": `Late at night when you're driving home and no one else is on the roads, And you come to a stoplight.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2074.315_2076.422.mp3`, "text": `And the stoplight is... I'm stopping.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2077.123_2078.164.mp3`, "text": `You're going to stop, right?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2078.204_2080.425.mp3`, "text": `But then you're sitting at the stoplight and you feel like...` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2082.505_2084.906.mp3`, "text": `You're going to wait that stoplight out.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2084.946_2086.607.mp3`, "text": `You anticipate where I'm going with this.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2087.587_2088.848.mp3`, "text": `You're going to sit at that stoplight.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2088.908_2092.228.mp3`, "text": `If it's a malfunctioning stoplight, you will be there in the morning.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_209.306_210.567.mp3`, "text": `Has this show started already?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_210.587_211.487.mp3`, "text": `This is the show.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2101.932_2102.252.mp3`, "text": `Okay.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2102.332_2102.632.mp3`, "text": `All right.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2102.672_2102.852.mp3`, "text": `Good.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2103.772_2103.952.mp3`, "text": `Good.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2107.595_2111.157.mp3`, "text": `Uh, I frequently do not stop at stoplights, even in the middle of the day.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2112.838_2113.378.mp3`, "text": `That's bad.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2113.558_2119.881.mp3`, "text": `I make a, I make a, I make a, I appraise the situation as I approach the intersection and I make a, I make an independent decision.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_212.707_213.908.mp3`, "text": `We're in it?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2121.982_2127.545.mp3`, "text": `Not a suggestion, but the light is there for a reason and it's controlled by, you know, it's part of a system.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2128.925_2129.726.mp3`, "text": `And that system.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2132.167_2132.967.mp3`, "text": `I'm part of a system.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2133.027_2134.108.mp3`, "text": `We're all part of the system.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2134.128_2134.608.mp3`, "text": `Right.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2134.868_2139.092.mp3`, "text": `And the light is there and it's doing a job and I respect the job it's doing.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2139.352_2144.617.mp3`, "text": `And I respect the people who are there to make sure that...` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_214.048_214.528.mp3`, "text": `We've begun?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2147.54_2148.401.mp3`, "text": `Oh, no, not at all.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2148.421_2149.281.mp3`, "text": `I'm grateful for them.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2150.743_2160.772.mp3`, "text": `But I also do not feel like... I do not feel that a stoplight... It isn't the stoplight that has authority, right?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_216.349_219.23.mp3`, "text": `Some kind of ABC News sports.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2162.228_2173.136.mp3`, "text": `just as it is not the police officer that has authority, it is the system that has authority and it is, and that authority is vested in the system by us and by our agreement.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2174.697_2184.345.mp3`, "text": `And so that understanding, you know, enables you to make reasonable and prudent decisions.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2185.245_2199.591.mp3`, "text": `to sometimes take some of that authority back and for a moment or two and say, I am vesting in myself the authority to ignore this stoplight because of reasons.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_219.25_219.47.mp3`, "text": `Yeah.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2200.131_2204.053.mp3`, "text": `Because I can see four miles in every direction and there's no one else here.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2205.873_2214.568.mp3`, "text": `And it is somewhat of an indignity to be stopped by a machine that Yeah.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2215.149_2228.735.mp3`, "text": `Which has no self-awareness and is stopping me only because it's on a program when I can make an independent determination for myself that it is very safe for me to continue making progress along this road.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2230.156_2244.857.mp3`, "text": `And so that amount, I mean, you know, it's a flexible amount of autonomy that I have to, that I grant myself within an overall system that I am fully aware vested in.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2245.978_2264.269.mp3`, "text": `I do believe that for the most part it is prudent to obey the police but that the police are agents of a collective agreement and in and of themselves do not.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2264.509_2270.873.mp3`, "text": `they are not power centers themselves they are agents they're representatives of a power that you know.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2271.854_2284.568.mp3`, "text": `that is our mutual uh decision to promote peace not steal from each other and stop at stoplights and so forth right?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2285.548_2286.628.mp3`, "text": `so yeah i do i?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2286.828_2287.408.mp3`, "text": `i retain.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2287.428_2293.13.mp3`, "text": `i retain to myself a certain amount of agency that may be.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2295.151_2297.751.mp3`, "text": `well that i hope everyone reserves for themselves.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2298.331_2309.385.mp3`, "text": `right i don't i don't flaunt it But you have to retain a little bit of your own freedom.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2311.186_2312.847.mp3`, "text": `And I think that that contributes to...` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2315.949_2316.73.mp3`, "text": `No, no, no.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2316.99_2340.407.mp3`, "text": `I think more to the point it is like it's a... In a way, it shows or it makes my acquiescence to the larger... body of rules more informed and more more actual because it isn't reflexive it isn't.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2341.308_2346.112.mp3`, "text": `i'm not uh i'm not doing it out of rote like it's.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2361.518_2400.731.mp3`, "text": `Well, yeah, an awareness or an acknowledgement that these things are not imposed upon us by an authority we can't comprehend, but are really mutual agreements, and mutual agreements that are invested, that I am invested in, and not... a slave to not an unthinking pawn, but, but, but a conscious, aware and engaged and involved person.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_237.982_242.664.mp3`, "text": `But that's also kind of a, who wants to be a millionaire sound.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2401.586_2409.551.mp3`, "text": `And so, yes, I believe that, you know, I believe that these laws... And part of it is that you have to think of every law and think like, why is this?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2409.711_2410.791.mp3`, "text": `Why do we have this law?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2412.212_2412.953.mp3`, "text": `And that's fun.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2413.133_2417.295.mp3`, "text": `That should be fun to figure out why there are laws.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2417.355_2420.937.mp3`, "text": `And that's how you end up understanding what taxes are for.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2421.037_2426.06.mp3`, "text": `because there are lots and lots of people in America that just don't like the idea of taxes.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2426.28_2426.641.mp3`, "text": `Yes.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2426.741_2447.113.mp3`, "text": `And so they go to war with... or with America or they sit and they stew and are bitter and maybe those people would always stop at stoplights, but they are plotting armed rebellion against the Obama administration because they don't like the idea of taxes.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_243.565_249.648.mp3`, "text": `Well, shouldn't we, before we launch right into the gender differences in apologizing.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2448.357_2458.692.mp3`, "text": `But if you think about why we tax and what the purpose of taxing is, and you recognize like, oh yeah, of course that system is incomplete.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2459.493_2465.203.mp3`, "text": `And of course there are opportunities for people to abuse it, but more often... more often.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2465.663_2474.027.mp3`, "text": `you know the taxation system is just so big and it has to fulfill so many obligations that it just it's.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2474.327_2475.187.mp3`, "text": `it's a creaky.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2475.207_2486.152.mp3`, "text": `you know bureaucracies are creaky not because they are not because of malice but just because because we're so frail and people are so fallible.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2487.777_2491.139.mp3`, "text": `But you think, yes, of course, I want the things that taxes buy.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2491.559_2496.462.mp3`, "text": `And I recognize that we all benefit from collective work.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2496.542_2500.324.mp3`, "text": `And so, yes, taxes, I get it and I pay them.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_250.789_254.27.mp3`, "text": `Which I'm guessing is going to be a major theme of the show.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2500.344_2503.646.mp3`, "text": `And does it hurt a little bit?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2503.726_2504.166.mp3`, "text": `Yes.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2504.447_2505.667.mp3`, "text": `Am I mad a little bit?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2505.727_2506.088.mp3`, "text": `Yes.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2506.928_2510.21.mp3`, "text": `But I understand and agree.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2512.157_2519.362.mp3`, "text": `And, you know, and the same is true all the way down to stop signs in the middle of nowhere.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2519.462_2525.766.mp3`, "text": `And the same is true scaled all the way up to like the big adventure of a U.S.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2526.227_2530.009.mp3`, "text": `expansionist military foreign policy.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2531.07_2533.271.mp3`, "text": `Where it's like, ah, that's not how I would do it.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2534.592_2539.916.mp3`, "text": `But I do see, you know, like my mom, for instance, does not believe in the army anymore.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_254.33_257.951.mp3`, "text": `But before we jump right in, shouldn't we introduce our show to people?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2541.095_2542.616.mp3`, "text": `She does not think there should be armies.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2544.317_2546.198.mp3`, "text": `And I understand where she's coming from.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2547.179_2550.461.mp3`, "text": `And we have long arguments about it and have for many years.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2551.141_2552.762.mp3`, "text": `But I do understand why there's an army.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2553.863_2568.712.mp3`, "text": `And I can't convince her why there's an army because she feels it the same way some people do about taxes, that you should just start by eliminating the army and then figure out other ways to solve it.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2570.133_2572.955.mp3`, "text": `the problems that we, that we feel we need armies to solve.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2579.18_2580.741.mp3`, "text": `Or there's not a lot of yelling.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_258.031_261.832.mp3`, "text": `This is a new enterprise.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2581.361_2589.547.mp3`, "text": `Uh, but she's, uh, you know, she, my, my mom who is, is much more radical than I am and always has been.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2590.068_2614.49.mp3`, "text": `She believes in, um, universal guaranteed income, which I'm not, I haven't made a decision about one way or the other and I, I understand it, but you know, it's the, um, it's the, it boils down to all these systems, Venn diagrams of systems overlapping systems overlapping.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_26.335_31.997.mp3`, "text": `You don't want to start off a conversation by saying things are just as middling as always.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2615.37_2632.941.mp3`, "text": `And, and every system would work perfectly if all it had to do was obey its own rules and, And so that's why socialism seems so appealing to socialists and why libertarianism seems so appealing to libertarians.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2633.701_2641.006.mp3`, "text": `is that within the confines of their circle, yeah, all those things, libertarianism would work perfectly.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2641.842_2644.204.mp3`, "text": `if it never had to interact with any other system.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_265.052_267.093.mp3`, "text": `Well, the thing is, you know more about this than I do.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2662.735_2666.077.mp3`, "text": `Because as soon as, and this is socialism, it's the same exact thing.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2666.137_2689.835.mp3`, "text": `As soon as you encounter one person who says, for whatever personal reason, says, I prefer not to, then the whole system breaks down because either you force that person to conform, in which case, whatever your economic theory, it's now overlapping a Venn diagram of authoritarianism.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_267.153_275.115.mp3`, "text": `I've only ever had one podcast where, I mean, my impression is that you have sixty podcasts?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2691.177_2693.399.mp3`, "text": `Or you don't force that person to conform.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2693.439_2704.767.mp3`, "text": `You either try to convince them to conform, which is liberalism, or you allow them to be outside of your system, in which case, little by little, your system falls apart.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2705.407_2716.635.mp3`, "text": `Because if one person's outside of it, then the second person is, and then a third person is, and pretty soon, the rules of your closed system don't apply.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2717.59_2729.073.mp3`, "text": `So that awareness or that sort of daily consciousness, I guess in me it promotes an understanding that we're actually doing the best we can right now.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2729.454_2733.255.mp3`, "text": `The system that we have is a three-legged dog.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2733.675_2736.316.mp3`, "text": `It is a broken transmission.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2736.396_2739.016.mp3`, "text": `It is all these terrible things.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2739.036_2743.518.mp3`, "text": `It does have excesses and abuses threaded into it.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2744.138_2760.967.mp3`, "text": `But as soon as you monkey with one aspect of it, you either have to say, well, in order to apply this, we are going to become an authoritarian society of one sort or another.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_276.075_276.495.mp3`, "text": `Sixteen.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2762.468_2771.813.mp3`, "text": `Or we're going to squeeze the balloon over here and over on this other side, it's going to have unintended consequences we didn't foresee.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2773.315_2776.357.mp3`, "text": `And then we're going to be putting out fires over there and putting out fires over there.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2776.818_2780.24.mp3`, "text": `And that's kind of what we're doing already.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2785.884_2790.948.mp3`, "text": `And what that all boils down to is that every once in a while in the middle of the night, I run a stop sign and I feel good about it.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2792.169_2794.371.mp3`, "text": `And I say, this is my little contribution.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2794.671_2795.131.mp3`, "text": `Right.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2795.432_2801.996.mp3`, "text": `And I do it partly to pay myself back for all the stop signs I do stop at.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2803.357_2814.045.mp3`, "text": `But partly to say, like, I agree with the laws for the most part, and I agree with them in principle, and I agree with them in spirit.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2815.367_2818.089.mp3`, "text": `And I guess that's what it is.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2818.409_2824.153.mp3`, "text": `To practice the spirit of the law is more important than to practice the letter of the law.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_282.562_283.603.mp3`, "text": `Let me ask you this.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2827.568_2830.99.mp3`, "text": `And so to practice the spirit of the law, sometimes you flout the letter of the law.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2836.913_2838.254.mp3`, "text": `No, I do not feel that.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2838.374_2846.498.mp3`, "text": `I feel like I am capable of making a determination that in the middle of the night, in the middle of town, when I can see for four miles in every direction...` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_284.344_287.928.mp3`, "text": `At peak podcast, how many podcasts were you doing?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2851.321_2851.921.mp3`, "text": `Well, sure.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2851.961_2859.025.mp3`, "text": `But I mean, if you're sitting at an intersection and you look left... And you see the traffic lights green into the distance.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2859.065_2859.325.mp3`, "text": `Right.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2893.097_2895.478.mp3`, "text": `Oh, well, that's the old bad part of town problem.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2895.518_2895.938.mp3`, "text": `Yeah.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2896.178_2897.839.mp3`, "text": `It's the Cabrini-Green problem.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2899.059_2906.202.mp3`, "text": `I remember a police officer pulled up next to me as I was driving through Cabrini-Green in Chicago at some point in the late eighties.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2907.103_2914.526.mp3`, "text": `And I was sitting at a stoplight and a police officer pulled up next to me and rolled his window down and said, don't stop at stoplights around here.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2916.031_2917.052.mp3`, "text": `And I was like, seriously?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2917.072_2919.613.mp3`, "text": `That's a fucked up thing to say.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2919.633_2924.836.mp3`, "text": `In that case, I'm going to sit at this stoplight.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2925.096_2926.356.mp3`, "text": `I'm taking it into my own hands.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2933.604_2944.291.mp3`, "text": `Well, because that is a, I mean, that's a, I have spent a lot of time in my life in neighborhoods where I was, where conventional wisdom said, don't go.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2945.051_2946.052.mp3`, "text": `Don't go into this neighborhood.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2946.092_2948.393.mp3`, "text": `Don't, you know, don't do this thing.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2949.194_2949.374.mp3`, "text": `Right.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2949.434_2951.515.mp3`, "text": `And that is, that's a kind of.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2953.516_2955.037.mp3`, "text": `It makes me super mad.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2955.317_2956.358.mp3`, "text": `And so, no, I do.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2956.598_2962.742.mp3`, "text": `I do go into the neighborhood and have benefited greatly from it.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2964.67_2972.814.mp3`, "text": `from sitting at a stoplight where, where the, even the police are like running the lights because they don't want to sit in idle.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2974.094_2975.015.mp3`, "text": `But that's, you know, do` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_2982.558_2982.918.mp3`, "text": `size` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3039.596_3046.882.mp3`, "text": `I was picked on a lot, but I didn't get big until I was... a junior in high school.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3048.263_3051.285.mp3`, "text": `I was, you know, because I, I started kindergarten when I was four.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_305.135_305.835.mp3`, "text": `Two a day.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_305.895_306.896.mp3`, "text": `That's incredible.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3051.365_3053.426.mp3`, "text": `So I was always a year younger.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3053.526_3053.966.mp3`, "text": `Right.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3060.931_3070.857.mp3`, "text": `Well, maybe I was appropriately sized, uh, as a kid, as you know, like the same size as other kids, but I was a, I was emotionally much smaller.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3072.178_3082.239.mp3`, "text": `And so I was pretty vulnerable, uh, kid until I got to be a junior and then all of a sudden was just much bigger.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_308.917_311.119.mp3`, "text": `So let me ask you this.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3082.259_3084.761.mp3`, "text": `and it all happened really fast.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3093.389_3097.953.mp3`, "text": `I started wearing them when I was in high school, freshman or sophomore.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3097.973_3098.274.mp3`, "text": `Yeah.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3099.785_3122.323.mp3`, "text": `But the privilege you're describing of being big and white, I have spent many years reflecting upon because I've done a lot of things in the world or I walk through the world like in a mantle of big white American guy.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3123.42_3129.142.mp3`, "text": `And it has protected me like a coat of armor for decades.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3129.262_3130.903.mp3`, "text": `And I wasn't always aware of it.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3131.483_3141.106.mp3`, "text": `I think when I was young, like, I mean, in my early twenties and mid twenties, I still felt like a vulnerable child inside.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3141.906_3159.284.mp3`, "text": `And so wasn't aware how much access I had by being, you know, like just what I said earlier about understanding that the police are are agents of an authority, but they themselves do not have any authority over me individually.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3159.304_3162.366.mp3`, "text": `That is a very privileged position.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3164.007_3169.57.mp3`, "text": `That I can, you know, that has a lot more to do with my whiteness than it does my size.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3171.391_3173.812.mp3`, "text": `Where a police officer comes up and says, you can't stand here.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3174.252_3175.673.mp3`, "text": `And I say, I beg your pardon.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3176.313_3177.374.mp3`, "text": `But in fact, I can.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3177.394_3177.474.mp3`, "text": `Yeah.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3178.43_3182.132.mp3`, "text": `And that's almost entirely a white privilege thing rather than a size privilege.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_318.304_319.245.mp3`, "text": `Let me put this to you.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3183.252_3194.376.mp3`, "text": `But the size and also the privilege of being, uh, of, of gender in terms of being able to walk around and, and, um, be in the wrong neighborhood at the wrong time.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_319.966_322.948.mp3`, "text": `This is a new podcast that you are introducing into the world.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3195.677_3215.993.mp3`, "text": `Uh, those are all, uh, all, I mean, an awareness of that was dawning over the course of, of a few decades, uh, And it's a powerful, I mean, it is a powerful set of privileges that I'm able to apply.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_32.077_32.357.mp3`, "text": `Yeah.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_32.817_34.558.mp3`, "text": `You want to say, yes, amazing.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3217.294_3228.259.mp3`, "text": `And what it does is it, I mean, primarily, I do not assert that I have any more right to the armrest than the small person sitting next to me.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3229.0_3248.232.mp3`, "text": `Because I recognize that the indignity of things not being built to suit me pales in comparison to the great opportunities I'm afforded by precisely those factors.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_324.245_337.404.mp3`, "text": `What makes you feel like this is a podcast that, I mean, once we're doing ten a day, now you have windowed that back, and now you are beginning a new podcast.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3248.692_3251.313.mp3`, "text": `And the loud husky voice helps.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3253.333_3256.514.mp3`, "text": `And also the thousand-yard stare that I've cultivated for many years.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3258.614_3259.534.mp3`, "text": `The steely resolve.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3259.694_3261.714.mp3`, "text": `And the fact... You know what my biggest privilege is?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3263.055_3266.969.mp3`, "text": `The fact that my parents... always laughed at my jokes.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3267.87_3269.77.mp3`, "text": `Like, genuinely laughed at my humor.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3271.11_3279.692.mp3`, "text": `My parents were interested in what I had to say, weren't pretending, weren't feigning an interest.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3279.732_3284.193.mp3`, "text": `But from a very young age, they thought I was funny and they thought I was interesting.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3287.274_3287.674.mp3`, "text": `It does.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3287.954_3302.735.mp3`, "text": `And that is the primary reason like the privilege that I, that I had from a young age because it taught me that I was interesting and, and worth listening to.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3303.815_3317.139.mp3`, "text": `And that's not a, that's not a thing that, I mean, you know, culturally, whether people think that I'm interesting or whether people listen more to big white men than they do to other people, like that's definitely a factor.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3317.879_3328.124.mp3`, "text": `But the primary factor was that my folks were, When I was six years old and tried to make a joke and say something funny, my folks were like, ha ha, good.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3329.604_3334.185.mp3`, "text": `And that gave me more power.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3334.966_3339.187.mp3`, "text": `It gave me more sense of my capability and my belonging in the world.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3339.807_3347.969.mp3`, "text": `Like the world itself has never really said unequivocally like, John Roderick, you belong.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3349.733_3354.657.mp3`, "text": `The world is pretty ambivalent about whether I belong.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3354.777_3361.101.mp3`, "text": `The world doesn't necessarily like my approach, but my folks always did.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3361.822_3366.465.mp3`, "text": `And so somewhere in me, there is a feeling that, yes, absolutely, I belong.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3366.585_3374.571.mp3`, "text": `And if I walk into a room and everyone in there despises me, I still feel like they can't keep me out.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_338.387_340.309.mp3`, "text": `What is going on?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3383.501_3385.402.mp3`, "text": `First sponsor, first episode.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3386.123_3389.265.mp3`, "text": `I can't wait to hear who they are and what their product is.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3392.166_3396.969.mp3`, "text": `Warby Parker, the glasses frame manufacturer?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_340.569_343.411.mp3`, "text": `Why introduce a new podcast into a world of podcasts?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3400.572_3401.092.mp3`, "text": `Okay, go ahead.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3442.893_3445.915.mp3`, "text": `I said well sounds like a cool guy sounds like your friend is a cool friend.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_346.594_349.417.mp3`, "text": `A lot of podcasts.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_349.437_356.022.mp3`, "text": `And this is one where you and I, two middle-aged white guys, are talking to each other long distance.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3541.225_3544.947.mp3`, "text": `See, once again, evidence that God is playing a prank.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3546.648_3551.192.mp3`, "text": `He has one of your eyes rotated just slightly out of kilter.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3551.552_3553.514.mp3`, "text": `It's a bad joke.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_357.504_357.864.mp3`, "text": `Why?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3570.741_3571.282.mp3`, "text": `High index.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_358.885_361.427.mp3`, "text": `Why, Dan Benjamin?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_36.059_39.202.mp3`, "text": `today today is the first day of the rest of our life.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3605.609_3605.829.mp3`, "text": `Me?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3607.53_3608.191.mp3`, "text": `You're asking me?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3608.311_3608.511.mp3`, "text": `Yes.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3608.531_3608.611.mp3`, "text": `Okay.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3609.96_3626.061.mp3`, "text": `So I have a very complicated relationship with Warby Parker because for many, many years... The only way to get the kind of glasses that I prefer was to buy vintage glasses.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3626.581_3636.487.mp3`, "text": `And that required a lot of work sorting through bins and visiting strange people in weird parts of town.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3637.247_3648.294.mp3`, "text": `And sometimes you would find an old... optometrist where they still had a bunch of vintage frames in the basement but the old man that was running the place didn't really want to go down there.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3648.414_3652.216.mp3`, "text": `you could talk him into it go down and find a thing.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3652.256_3660.675.mp3`, "text": `and you know I bought so many pairs of vintage glasses and Where it still had the original price tag on it from the fifties and sixties.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3660.775_3669.0.mp3`, "text": `And, and, and then when you would get lenses put in them, you always were worried that the plastic was, had decayed and was going to crack.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3669.9_3682.808.mp3`, "text": `So when I was out in the world roaming around the streets of America and Europe, and I would see someone at a distance wearing a pair of glasses, which I, I instantly identified as vintage glasses.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3683.288_3690.674.mp3`, "text": `That person would also see me wearing, And I knew how much work they'd put into that and they knew how much work I'd put into it.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3691.114_3693.776.mp3`, "text": `So we would nod and sometimes even stop and talk.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3694.416_3708.024.mp3`, "text": `I remember one time in a cafe in Hamburg, the guy behind the counter was wearing a pair of glasses, which I... coveted and knew were very special.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3708.104_3719.247.mp3`, "text": `and I said those glasses and he said yeah well I found them in Berlin from a man with a special place and he had a dog and it was a red dog.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3719.448_3731.651.mp3`, "text": `and we had this long conversation about the great adventure he'd gone on to find this particular pair of frames and I'm always telling the story of the glasses I'm wearing and so forth.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3731.691_3738.803.mp3`, "text": `it was always a a real indicator of a certain kind of person.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3740.484_3749.607.mp3`, "text": `and warby parker's frames are all designed very much according to the principles of like vintage.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3749.707_3753.148.mp3`, "text": `yeah for sure they look very very classic.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3753.648_3772.484.mp3`, "text": `and so just a few years ago when warby parker came on the scene I was suddenly in this position where I would see somebody in an airport or in a grocery store and I would see their glasses and feel like, here is an entree to talk to this person.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_376.472_377.233.mp3`, "text": `Multimodal.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_377.934_378.394.mp3`, "text": `Right.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3772.524_3776.607.mp3`, "text": `And I would walk up to them and say, your glasses, they're extraordinary.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3777.188_3778.569.mp3`, "text": `Tell me about that.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3779.149_3784.714.mp3`, "text": `And the person would look at me shocked and say, they're Warby Parker.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_378.915_380.096.mp3`, "text": `Multimodal communication.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3784.994_3787.476.mp3`, "text": `And I would go, oh, oh, I'm sorry.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3787.636_3789.178.mp3`, "text": `I'm sorry I interrupted your day.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3789.238_3791.479.mp3`, "text": `Like, you know, you're free to go.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3791.499_3799.054.mp3`, "text": `I just thought, because at any other time in my life, I would have... You know, marched up to this person and gone, your glasses, tell me about them.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3799.094_3801.614.mp3`, "text": `And they would have said in nineteen seventy nine.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_380.296_380.676.mp3`, "text": `Yeah.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3802.134_3805.955.mp3`, "text": `I was in, you know, I was in the deserts of Sumaria and so forth.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3807.395_3810.016.mp3`, "text": `So it has changed my social equation.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3810.096_3817.258.mp3`, "text": `now because I see people in the world wearing glasses that, you know, that I spent twenty five years.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3817.318_3818.798.mp3`, "text": `I spent thirty years wearing.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3819.79_3827.095.mp3`, "text": `training myself to see these see a certain kind of frame and know what it meant.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3827.315_3830.197.mp3`, "text": `yeah and now it means a different thing now.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3830.757_3833.579.mp3`, "text": `now regular people have access to these frames.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3834.24_3836.041.mp3`, "text": `regular people have access to these styles.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3836.121_3842.365.mp3`, "text": `people who do not want to be in the basement of a optometrist in chinatown and that is very complicated.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3842.785_3845.327.mp3`, "text": `so i have never had a pair of warby parker glasses.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3846.623_3848.764.mp3`, "text": `But I'm ready.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3849.244_3849.665.mp3`, "text": `I'm ready.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3850.205_3860.45.mp3`, "text": `I'm ready to go through the looking glass and try on and take the risk and have the adventure.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3861.411_3866.614.mp3`, "text": `Have the adventure of this new way into this look.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3867.414_3871.216.mp3`, "text": `So now I can walk up to somebody in an airport and say, are those Warby Parkers?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3871.456_3872.297.mp3`, "text": `And they're going to look at me and go...` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3874.018_3876.5.mp3`, "text": `And we're going to have like a, it's a new way of sharing.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3876.54_3876.661.mp3`, "text": `Right.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3881.164_3886.929.mp3`, "text": `I'm, I'm, I'm, you know, I'm ready to bloom and grow, bloom and grow forever.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3897.599_3898.259.mp3`, "text": `All right.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_39.222_45.069.mp3`, "text": `yeah lives life has given us lemons and what do we do?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3954.621_3955.421.mp3`, "text": `Landscaping lights.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_3955.501_3956.282.mp3`, "text": `Landscaping lights.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_398.061_399.222.mp3`, "text": `Let's go all the way.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_399.262_400.382.mp3`, "text": `Let's say what we need to say.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4006.974_4007.935.mp3`, "text": `Yes.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4044.571_4046.272.mp3`, "text": `You've got a rhyme and a reason.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4142.809_4148.196.mp3`, "text": `No, I do not have... Very many routines.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_415.549_425.017.mp3`, "text": `Hundreds and hundreds of thousands of people shared your reticence and also have been waiting to listen to the show.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4171.303_4183.872.mp3`, "text": `I'm a person probably like a lot of our listeners, just a normal person who does not like to go to sleep and also does not like to wake up.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4185.332_4189.295.mp3`, "text": `So when it's time to go to sleep, I do everything I can to avoid going to sleep.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4190.376_4207.962.mp3`, "text": `I sit and read until I'm too exhausted to hold up my... book and then i go downstairs and get a drink of water and then maybe i'll take a little handful of popcorn and then i'll go back upstairs and lay down and maybe i'll play solitaire on my phone for a while.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4208.002_4212.626.mp3`, "text": `whatever it is i hate to finally succumb.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4213.227_4218.931.mp3`, "text": `turn off the light roll over go to sleep and i will stay up for hours and hours rather than um.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4222.165_4226.728.mp3`, "text": `rather than just make the decision, now it is time for sleep.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4228.048_4236.613.mp3`, "text": `And so I never go to sleep at a regular time because I'm always trying to push that boundary, just push it a little bit further.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4236.974_4240.696.mp3`, "text": `I can read two more pages of this book, just a little longer.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4241.196_4243.377.mp3`, "text": `I don't know why that is true.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4243.517_4245.839.mp3`, "text": `I just don't like to give up.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4247.66_4255.89.mp3`, "text": `And then once I... have turned off the light and am sleeping.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_425.318_427.7.mp3`, "text": `Literally millions of people.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4257.451_4259.772.mp3`, "text": `I love being asleep.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4260.133_4262.994.mp3`, "text": `And in the morning when it's time to wake up, I do not want to wake up.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4264.475_4267.937.mp3`, "text": `I want to roll over and go back to sleep as long as I possibly can.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4268.057_4275.722.mp3`, "text": `So I will first become kind of awake and aware at seven or eight o'clock in the morning.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4275.762_4278.443.mp3`, "text": `And I will say, oh, that's terrible.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4278.803_4279.944.mp3`, "text": `Seven o'clock in the morning.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4280.284_4281.425.mp3`, "text": `Awful, awful times.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4282.2_4283.601.mp3`, "text": `And I'll roll over and go back to sleep.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4283.701_4285.963.mp3`, "text": `And then it'll be eight and then it'll be nine.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4285.983_4288.365.mp3`, "text": `And I will keep doing that.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4288.906_4293.049.mp3`, "text": `And at a certain point, the idea enters into my mind that now it's late.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4293.189_4295.851.mp3`, "text": `Now I have slept too long.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4298.153_4305.74.mp3`, "text": `And my reaction to that is generally to try and put that feeling out of my mind by rolling over and going back to sleep again.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4305.76_4305.84.mp3`, "text": `Okay.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4306.833_4317.762.mp3`, "text": `And depending on where I am in my bipolar cycle, I sometimes will sleep until one o'clock in the afternoon by that method.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_431.984_433.485.mp3`, "text": `Have been waiting and waiting.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4318.822_4327.347.mp3`, "text": `And other times, you know, at nine o'clock in the morning, I finally have enough to do, have enough scheduled that I have to get up.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4327.427_4333.05.mp3`, "text": `So for instance, this morning, I knew that I had a podcast with you at a certain point.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4333.71_4337.392.mp3`, "text": `But also, my daughter has to get up and go to school in the morning.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4337.452_4344.696.mp3`, "text": `So I wake up, I get her up and going to school.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_434.446_437.108.mp3`, "text": `It's on their to-do list, I hope, I presume.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4344.796_4352.18.mp3`, "text": `And that is a thing that, you know, is... I have help from my mom in doing.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4352.261_4358.985.mp3`, "text": `And there are times when the burden of getting my daughter up and off to school falls entirely to me.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4359.566_4361.847.mp3`, "text": `And other times I have, it is a cooperative effort.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4362.488_4372.855.mp3`, "text": `And other times other people in my daughter's life get her up and get her to school and allow me to kind of sleep in because everybody in my family knows about this problem.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4374.036_4386.164.mp3`, "text": `But then back to sleep, I went and And slept until I was absolutely up against the deadline of needing to get up and come to my office to podcast with you.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4387.285_4397.154.mp3`, "text": `And so one of the ways I try and live a normal life is I schedule things at a certain hour in the morning where it requires that I be up like a regular person.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_439.03_439.891.mp3`, "text": `It's on their bucket list.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_439.951_442.293.mp3`, "text": `One of these days they're going to get around to listening to Roderick on the Line.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4397.734_4401.658.mp3`, "text": `But then I resent those appointments because they are forcing me up.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4403.895_4410.199.mp3`, "text": `Anyway, so every single day is different because every day has a first appointment.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4411.199_4413.22.mp3`, "text": `And sometimes that first appointment is eight a.m.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4413.26_4414.521.mp3`, "text": `and sometimes it's ten a.m.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4415.001_4420.544.mp3`, "text": `But I will sleep right up until the last possible moment, no matter what the rule is.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_442.373_443.774.mp3`, "text": `But you eventually did.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4421.845_4430.79.mp3`, "text": `And then making coffee of my own in the morning is very... It requires that I be up early enough to make coffee.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4432.291_4439.848.mp3`, "text": `And I always... would rather sleep until the last possible moment rather than get up and make a pot of coffee, even though I want coffee.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4442.59_4449.416.mp3`, "text": `So I tried to buy one of those coffee makers that was on a timer that would make the coffee for me, but that required that I do the work at night.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4450.417_4451.838.mp3`, "text": `And I didn't really want to do that either.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4453.451_4461.037.mp3`, "text": `And so you're starting to get a picture, I hope, of how burdensome I find almost everything.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4462.018_4473.567.mp3`, "text": `And what that means is that I'm always just being prodded along with the cattle prod of responsibility.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4474.987_4490.783.mp3`, "text": `And it moves me from one thing to the next, but never according to an architecture of a ritual or a scheme or a plan.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4491.524_4494.547.mp3`, "text": `It's always just an alarm is going off.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4495.47_4497.292.mp3`, "text": `And I've pushed the snooze button.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4498.213_4500.315.mp3`, "text": `And this is true in the day too, right?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_450.139_450.68.mp3`, "text": `Yeah, sure.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_450.72_451.861.mp3`, "text": `It was your prison podcast.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4500.395_4504.619.mp3`, "text": `It's right now, it's quarter till here.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4505.199_4509.123.mp3`, "text": `And I made some plan to meet somebody later.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4509.163_4514.268.mp3`, "text": `And I told them I would be there between a certain time and another time.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4515.709_4529.409.mp3`, "text": `And all of that is just an attempt to prod me on this sort of baton death March that is living a life.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_452.501_455.484.mp3`, "text": `Saving it for when you sailed your sailboat around the world.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4586.072_4587.994.mp3`, "text": `There are so many individual grapes.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4588.074_4591.678.mp3`, "text": `It's very hard to know if you have washed a bunch of grapes successfully.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_46.23_47.912.mp3`, "text": `suck on them and make a sour face.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4616.493_4622.538.mp3`, "text": `So it's a division of labor within your marriage that she shoulders the grape washing.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4623.639_4627.443.mp3`, "text": `And then you must do some correspondingly onerous task that she doesn't want.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4636.385_4636.585.mp3`, "text": `Yeah.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4647.094_4647.574.mp3`, "text": `Oh, is that right?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4647.614_4648.655.mp3`, "text": `You're a good scrambled egg maker?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4651.217_4651.397.mp3`, "text": `Yeah.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4651.457_4652.298.mp3`, "text": `I don't know how to make them.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4655.794_4656.674.mp3`, "text": `Well, see, this is the thing.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4656.714_4659.016.mp3`, "text": `It's not hard slash, but there are secrets to it.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4659.036_4661.297.mp3`, "text": `It's like, well, that sounds hard.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4663.199_4664.199.mp3`, "text": `You have to learn a secret.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4664.279_4667.501.mp3`, "text": `You have to get somebody to tell you a secret, first of all, and then you have to learn it.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4672.304_4673.745.mp3`, "text": `Everybody likes scrambled eggs.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4673.865_4676.087.mp3`, "text": `Find me a person that doesn't like scrambled eggs.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4678.192_4683.597.mp3`, "text": `But I don't – I put a little milk in them.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4683.657_4684.778.mp3`, "text": `I put a little water in them.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4684.918_4685.699.mp3`, "text": `I whip them up.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4685.899_4688.281.mp3`, "text": `I set the stove.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4688.401_4691.564.mp3`, "text": `I make them, and then they always burn and are dry.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_471.46_477.942.mp3`, "text": `You know, this is a common, it's a common plot device for, for films, guy on a boat and things keep getting worse.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4754.758_4756.678.mp3`, "text": `Do you go to a psychologist?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4758.619_4759.46.mp3`, "text": `Have you in the past?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4759.52_4759.78.mp3`, "text": `Yes.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4761.878_4765.08.mp3`, "text": `And what did that psychologist tell you?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4770.803_4771.283.mp3`, "text": `Oh, really?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4772.124_4777.985.mp3`, "text": `You've... You've solved your generalized anxiety by organizing all of the...` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_478.042_481.203.mp3`, "text": `But you're talking about the Robert Redford, Robert Redford film.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4795.179_4795.719.mp3`, "text": `Namaste.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4798.342_4801.924.mp3`, "text": `And now you feel like you're on top of it.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_48.012_50.795.mp3`, "text": `no make lemonade.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4814.516_4815.517.mp3`, "text": `All right.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4815.537_4816.377.mp3`, "text": `Tell me how you do the eggs.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4823.362_4823.462.mp3`, "text": `Okay.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4823.482_4823.783.mp3`, "text": `All right.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4830.173_4836.738.mp3`, "text": `So I would be making eggs for between two and three people, but I would always make enough eggs for four people.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4836.758_4837.659.mp3`, "text": `Okay.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4838.019_4841.802.mp3`, "text": `Because I have a general principle, which is make all the bacon.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4842.983_4843.163.mp3`, "text": `Right.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4843.344_4843.504.mp3`, "text": `Yep.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4843.704_4846.686.mp3`, "text": `And so make all the bacon also includes make eggs for four.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4847.727_4848.968.mp3`, "text": `So I'm very curious.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4848.988_4854.752.mp3`, "text": `And also we should, we should stay that making scrambled eggs is a, one of the most universal things.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4855.773_4858.515.mp3`, "text": `Everyone has done it and seen it done a thousand times.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4859.155_4871.961.mp3`, "text": `So for you to be now venturing a secret system or a better way of making scrambled eggs, it is like saying, here is a new way to wipe yourself when you have gone potty.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4873.202_4873.342.mp3`, "text": `Right?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4873.362_4874.383.mp3`, "text": `It's a thing that we all do.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4874.683_4875.043.mp3`, "text": `Yeah.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4875.343_4875.883.mp3`, "text": `All the time.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4876.364_4878.625.mp3`, "text": `Everybody's presumably got their own way of doing it.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4879.625_4883.968.mp3`, "text": `You are stepping into this arena and saying, no, there is a better way.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4885.333_4893.336.mp3`, "text": `And frankly, I wish somebody would come up with a better way to wipe yourself when you have gone potty because I don't feel like my method is any great shakes.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4896.757_4901.478.mp3`, "text": `I don't, you know, I feel like I'm just barely eking it out.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4901.919_4902.959.mp3`, "text": `I'm barely squeaking by.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4904.779_4906.76.mp3`, "text": `Yeah, it just feels like there's not a better way to do this.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4907.1_4911.152.mp3`, "text": `You know, the people that invented the wet wipes... They said, oh, here's a better way.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4911.232_4916.057.mp3`, "text": `And then they ruined the sewer systems of every city in America.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4916.077_4916.377.mp3`, "text": `Yeah.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4919.24_4920.06.mp3`, "text": `They're not flushable.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4920.381_4920.941.mp3`, "text": `Don't flush them.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4921.842_4923.223.mp3`, "text": `That's my public service announcement.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4923.944_4927.987.mp3`, "text": `But you're walking into this scrambled egg story.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4928.833_4939.219.mp3`, "text": `You're planting a flag, and you're saying, here it is, the definitive or one of a handful of definitive methods of doing this universal task.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4939.939_4941.14.mp3`, "text": `So I am all ears.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4941.32_4941.98.mp3`, "text": `Go.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4947.483_4947.784.mp3`, "text": `Wait a minute.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4947.824_4948.884.mp3`, "text": `You said it was easy.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4951.726_4951.926.mp3`, "text": `Okay.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4963.002_4964.362.mp3`, "text": `Oh, wait a minute.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4964.402_4965.483.mp3`, "text": `It requires a new kind of pan?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_4994.747_4998.969.mp3`, "text": `Plastic spatula, nonstick pan, maybe something called a green earth pan.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_50.935_55.76.mp3`, "text": `yeah at least that's my policy.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5025.378_5025.859.mp3`, "text": `It's okay.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5025.899_5026.679.mp3`, "text": `Don't fear the butter.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5055.529_5064.775.mp3`, "text": `this is not a fast system i'm about to tell you okay don't crank the heat medium eggs like medium medium heat or they'll get ropey right and you don't want a ropey egg.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_507.074_507.314.mp3`, "text": `Yeah.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5076.982_5079.384.mp3`, "text": `Well, you're the one that's making eggs for four people.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5079.464_5079.884.mp3`, "text": `Eight eggs.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5080.284_5080.945.mp3`, "text": `Eight eggs, all right.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5097.677_5098.117.mp3`, "text": `Wait a minute.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5099.599_5103.803.mp3`, "text": `This is the beginning of new ideas for me here.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5103.863_5104.664.mp3`, "text": `Now, what do you mean?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5104.684_5106.966.mp3`, "text": `You don't crack eggs on the corner of the bowl?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_514.077_525.46.mp3`, "text": `You would think that Robert Redford could afford the best medical care and that a team of doctors would have prevented him from getting swimmer's ear.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5160.094_5162.136.mp3`, "text": `introducing bacteria into the egg.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5185.308_5186.109.mp3`, "text": `I'm not a monster.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5201.434_5202.434.mp3`, "text": `Are you saying don't do that?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5205.795_5205.995.mp3`, "text": `Okay.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5206.295_5207.576.mp3`, "text": `You put them right in the compost.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5212.433_5213.234.mp3`, "text": `Texas compost.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5247.328_5247.588.mp3`, "text": `Right.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_526.64_528.541.mp3`, "text": `But in fact, we are so vulnerable.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5266.256_5266.876.mp3`, "text": `Flick the water.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5278.762_5279.263.mp3`, "text": `you want the.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5279.643_5280.643.mp3`, "text": `you want the water.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_528.621_535.543.mp3`, "text": `Humans are so vulnerable that even Robert Redford can suffer such an indignity.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5281.024_5285.086.mp3`, "text": `yes to dance around the pan yes now wait have you put the butter in?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5286.326_5288.067.mp3`, "text": `so you've got a dry hot pan.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5288.247_5293.39.mp3`, "text": `right non-stick yep potentially green earth pan.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5293.49_5297.617.mp3`, "text": `yeah You throw some water in it, and then you watch it dance.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5326.145_5327.105.mp3`, "text": `Okay, okay, good.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_535.563_535.983.mp3`, "text": `Right.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5350.813_5357.338.mp3`, "text": `So you're saying you're monkeying with these eggs from the moment that they hit the pan until they're out of the pan.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5357.418_5358.139.mp3`, "text": `Flip fold.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5360.64_5361.741.mp3`, "text": `With your plastic spatula.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5376.212_5377.453.mp3`, "text": `Don't stop before the eggs are done?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5392.84_5395.042.mp3`, "text": `They'll continue to cook once they're plated.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5395.102_5397.844.mp3`, "text": `So how do you know they are almost ready?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5419.442_5428.846.mp3`, "text": `Now, how about, I hate to, I hate to get into this, but how about introducing cheese or a diced ham or some other element?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5435.808_5438.63.mp3`, "text": `I take umbrage at characterizing it as wishy-washy.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_544.487_545.927.mp3`, "text": `Are you doing this research in advance?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5445.896_5447.256.mp3`, "text": `They called it wishy-washy?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5448.397_5450.459.mp3`, "text": `And you went to school in West Texas somewhere?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5452.36_5453.461.mp3`, "text": `Oh, Philadelphia.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5456.683_5457.884.mp3`, "text": `It was called wishy-washy.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5459.385_5460.065.mp3`, "text": `Scrambled...` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5462.287_5462.847.mp3`, "text": `Egg stuff.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5463.128_5463.228.mp3`, "text": `Yeah.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5464.088_5466.129.mp3`, "text": `Now, let me ask you this.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5466.53_5475.795.mp3`, "text": `When you take a cup and you go and you put a little bit of root beer and a little bit of Pepsi and a little bit of seven up and a little bit of orange crush in it, what do you call that?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_547.668_548.448.mp3`, "text": `That's incredible.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_548.488_550.408.mp3`, "text": `You are so good on computers.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5486.342_5486.683.mp3`, "text": `Did you...` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5492.367_5493.888.mp3`, "text": `Did you ever go roller skating?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_55.8_57.602.mp3`, "text": `starting starting starting off today.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5508.055_5509.717.mp3`, "text": `did you grow up in the nineteen forties?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5511.178_5516.762.mp3`, "text": `i was born in seventy two so they didn't have roller rinks where you know they did.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5521.246_5522.947.mp3`, "text": `you didn't get to go to the roller rink?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5528.871_5534.756.mp3`, "text": `what did kids do for birthday parties in the late nineteen seventies where you grew up in philadelphia?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5535.737_5541.956.mp3`, "text": `um Did you just go pitch pennies against a wall?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5545.159_5545.739.mp3`, "text": `Street hockey.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5548.622_5551.204.mp3`, "text": `Because you were growing up in Germantown or something.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5552.705_5554.246.mp3`, "text": `You literally were growing up in Germantown?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5558.529_5568.237.mp3`, "text": `Well, for those of us who grew up in sort of western suburban environments who were not growing up in some kind of John Waters film...` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_557.05_558.87.mp3`, "text": `I'm surprised.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5574.841_5592.813.mp3`, "text": `Yeah, I mean, you were back east in the decaying remnants of a nineteenth-century American city, trying to find amusement in a place that was ruled by various mafias and characterized by ingrained systemic racism.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_559.391_560.331.mp3`, "text": `I do subscribe to that.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5596.461_5603.116.mp3`, "text": `Out west, where the roads were wide and freedom was in the trees... Yeah.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_560.371_561.131.mp3`, "text": `I'm surprised I haven't.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5603.136_5613.459.mp3`, "text": `We had all these different options... but primarily a kid's social life in the nineteen seventies revolved around the roller rink.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_561.151_561.551.mp3`, "text": `You missed.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5613.86_5631.128.mp3`, "text": `right and you went to the roller rink at birthday parties and on Friday nights and they played blondie and and chic and the Bee Gees and And you rented a pair of roller skates.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_562.051_562.351.mp3`, "text": `Go ahead.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5631.148_5637.23.mp3`, "text": `You didn't have to buy them or clip on some like tin roller skates to your Converse tennis shoes.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5637.97_5640.691.mp3`, "text": `You rented roller skates and then you skated around.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5642.271_5656.438.mp3`, "text": `And the boys skated with the boys and the girls skated with the girls, unless it was couples skate, in which case you had to either get off the roller rink or or find someone to skate with as a couple.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5656.798_5657.319.mp3`, "text": `Right.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5680.699_5682.361.mp3`, "text": `But no, you're just a danger to everybody.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5684.122_5692.229.mp3`, "text": `But one of the primary things at a roller rink, because, you know, I'm speaking now as a ten-year-old in nineteen seventy eight.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5693.293_5697.957.mp3`, "text": `And you are at the roller rink, you are free, right?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5698.037_5703.242.mp3`, "text": `Your parents take you there and leave you because they don't want to be in this terrible environment.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_57.682_58.163.mp3`, "text": `how about you?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5704.723_5710.088.mp3`, "text": `And you are now alone, but in basically what amounts to a club, a nightclub.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5711.089_5715.133.mp3`, "text": `Where you are on roller skates and they are playing disco music.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5716.699_5718.842.mp3`, "text": `So you're experiencing all these things.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5718.862_5725.63.mp3`, "text": `You're experiencing the tension of the sexual politics of ten-year-olds.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5726.491_5729.134.mp3`, "text": `You're learning how to dance and also learning how to roller skate.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5729.154_5735.682.mp3`, "text": `But most importantly, you are in charge of your own soda pop experience.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5737.49_5742.953.mp3`, "text": `because at the roller rink, you would get a cup and then the soda pop machine was there.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5742.993_5750.858.mp3`, "text": `And it was the first, it was at least my first exposure to a pop machine, which you could access yourself.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5751.999_5755.361.mp3`, "text": `You didn't have to go to the soda fountain guy and say, give me a Coke.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5755.661_5756.862.mp3`, "text": `You could get your own Coke.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_576.739_577.2.mp3`, "text": `That's awful.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5761.325_5762.405.mp3`, "text": `No, absolutely.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5762.445_5762.946.mp3`, "text": `They were cigarette.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5765.027_5774.083.mp3`, "text": `Um, And so it was at the roller rink that I was introduced to the concept of making a pop where you did not just have one kind of pop.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5774.703_5780.805.mp3`, "text": `You went down the line and you put a little bit of every kind of pop in the cup.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5781.745_5788.968.mp3`, "text": `So you got some root beer, some orange, some Sprite, some... You skipped the diet, obviously.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5789.368_5792.149.mp3`, "text": `And I think at the time, maybe there wasn't even a diet pop.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5792.489_5792.969.mp3`, "text": `No, there was Tabb.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5795.837_5798.418.mp3`, "text": `And I like tabs, so you put a little tab in there.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5798.998_5800.599.mp3`, "text": `And it's a regionalism.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5802.019_5808.242.mp3`, "text": `Some people would call that a cemetery or a suicide.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5808.262_5809.762.mp3`, "text": `Okay, yeah.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5810.343_5811.783.mp3`, "text": `But we called it a graveyard.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5814.304_5828.767.mp3`, "text": `And what I was hoping to get... was that you guys in Philadelphia with your strange like Godfather Part Two version of the world.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5829.987_5833.528.mp3`, "text": `That you guys had some other weird name for a graveyard.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5833.648_5841.23.mp3`, "text": `But of course, I'm realizing that it was even weirder there that you were probably still drinking Moxie out of a bottle.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5848.611_5848.751.mp3`, "text": `No.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5848.991_5849.811.mp3`, "text": `What is a fluffer number?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_585.905_588.146.mp3`, "text": `So that movie had a profound effect on me too.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5850.432_5853.252.mp3`, "text": `See, we have some kind of, it's some kind of whipped cream thing.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5863.955_5866.975.mp3`, "text": `I think that you would put that in.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5867.836_5869.236.mp3`, "text": `What do you put marshmallow cream in?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5869.276_5872.477.mp3`, "text": `I think you, you mix it into some sort of dessert.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5873.661_5875.223.mp3`, "text": `uh i mean we had marshmallows.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_589.226_595.638.mp3`, "text": `Yeah, because that's a prime... That's a prime motivator, right?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5896.683_5899.065.mp3`, "text": `I can imagine what marshmallow cream is by the name.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5906.468_5906.689.mp3`, "text": `Okay.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5915.133_5915.834.mp3`, "text": `Peanut butter?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5925.735_5926.435.mp3`, "text": `On bread?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5931.278_5934.319.mp3`, "text": `Peanut butter and marshmallow cream on white bread.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5935.7_5936.48.mp3`, "text": `Oh, my God.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5946.169_5961.657.mp3`, "text": `So you'd stop playing stickball for a minute and Vinny would come out and turn the fire hydrant off so that you could get on your tin roller skates and skate home to the stoop where your mother would give you white bread with marshmallow fluff on it.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_596.799_598.179.mp3`, "text": `How am I going to spend the rest of my life?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5963.318_5964.398.mp3`, "text": `Good grief.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5969.973_5971.634.mp3`, "text": `Sure, get beat up on the way home.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5972.194_5979.576.mp3`, "text": `And then Serpico would squeal up and get into a fight with some pimp.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_598.219_603.881.mp3`, "text": `Well, at some point, I assume that I'm going to sail a sailboat around the world by myself.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5981.116_5984.977.mp3`, "text": `This whole thing, no wonder you escaped to Texas.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_5989.441_6001.312.mp3`, "text": `You know, out in the West, you know, in Alaska, most of the streets when I was a kid, most of the streets in the town outside of the center of town were not paved streets.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6001.373_6002.734.mp3`, "text": `They were dirt streets.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6003.415_6005.256.mp3`, "text": `So you couldn't roller skate on the streets.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6007.058_6012.944.mp3`, "text": `And you had to watch out for bulldozers, which were a big part of the traffic up there at the time.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6014.668_6017.25.mp3`, "text": `But no, there were no fluffernutters.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6017.39_6023.074.mp3`, "text": `And I still am trying to imagine it, and it sounds so repulsive.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6031.54_6032.661.mp3`, "text": `No, it sounds awful.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6041.171_6042.271.mp3`, "text": `It's not fancy enough?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6044.792_6045.473.mp3`, "text": `What do you add?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6045.513_6045.993.mp3`, "text": `Sprinkles?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6048.994_6049.815.mp3`, "text": `Come on.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6049.895_6051.235.mp3`, "text": `This is just, this is like some.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6056.498_6057.658.mp3`, "text": `That's Elvis food.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6074.543_6075.683.mp3`, "text": `This is pure Elvis food.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6075.723_6079.084.mp3`, "text": `And let me also state for the record, do not put sliced bananas in your pancakes.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6081.164_6082.965.mp3`, "text": `Well, I just don't approve of it.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6084.386_6091.067.mp3`, "text": `I feel like if you're going to have a pancake and you want a banana, that's fine.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6092.048_6094.368.mp3`, "text": `But why would you put bananas, sliced bananas?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6094.408_6096.949.mp3`, "text": `That's like putting sliced hot dogs in your macaroni and cheese.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6108.871_6109.372.mp3`, "text": `No, no.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6109.452_6110.492.mp3`, "text": `Keep those foods apart.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6113.796_6115.077.mp3`, "text": `Keep those foods apart.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6115.137_6117.639.mp3`, "text": `And frankly, no walnuts in fudge.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6118.96_6119.62.mp3`, "text": `Oh, right.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6122.142_6123.463.mp3`, "text": `No, don't put a walnut in that.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6123.483_6126.325.mp3`, "text": `I mean, if you want to have a handful of walnuts or whatever, that's fine.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6126.345_6127.846.mp3`, "text": `Or maybe you want walnuts on top.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6129.327_6133.27.mp3`, "text": `But, you know, you show up at somebody's house for Christmas fudge and they've got walnuts in it.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_613.103_613.903.mp3`, "text": `Justifiably.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6135.491_6136.492.mp3`, "text": `Come on, Grandma.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6137.012_6138.233.mp3`, "text": `Get the walnuts out of the fudge.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6138.273_6138.814.mp3`, "text": `It's terrible.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6143.586_6144.907.mp3`, "text": `Now, how many sponsors do we have?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6146.768_6147.028.mp3`, "text": `Okay.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6147.068_6147.328.mp3`, "text": `All right.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6147.348_6148.968.mp3`, "text": `So second sponsorship.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6151.629_6152.51.mp3`, "text": `This is all new to me.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6157.191_6157.712.mp3`, "text": `Who knows?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6157.772_6161.753.mp3`, "text": `Merlin doesn't share with me any of the inner workings of the show.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6162.113_6164.034.mp3`, "text": `He prefers to keep me in the dark.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6166.174_6168.136.mp3`, "text": `And that works for both of us.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6172.541_6180.91.mp3`, "text": `I'm seeing how the sausage is made here, and I can't wait to hear who the second glorious sponsor of the show is.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6181.17_6182.672.mp3`, "text": `I'm so pleased about them.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6187.744_6188.585.mp3`, "text": `Wealthfront?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6221.627_6224.228.mp3`, "text": `People told you that you would be a multibillionaire by the time you were forty?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_623.903_624.404.mp3`, "text": `I see.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_627.905_628.226.mp3`, "text": `Correct.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_628.246_629.166.mp3`, "text": `Could happen anytime.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_630.027_635.349.mp3`, "text": `She's assuming it's only when you're old and infirm, but you could leave on your fiftieth birthday.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6326.778_6329.059.mp3`, "text": `This is some real grown-up sponsorship stuff.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6334.445_6335.326.mp3`, "text": `Who is our audience?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6338.467_6339.207.mp3`, "text": `Agreed, agreed.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6387.37_6388.192.mp3`, "text": `Yes, absolutely.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6392.53_6392.79.mp3`, "text": `Yes.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6393.39_6395.131.mp3`, "text": `Yes, I'm suing everybody now.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6422.439_6428.768.mp3`, "text": `That little disclaimer that you read in a kind of hilariously fast and monotone disclaimer reading voice.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6430.009_6436.017.mp3`, "text": `I mean, I think I even have an app on my phone that could auto-tune the news.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6448.815_6449.036.mp3`, "text": `Right.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6457.013_6459.615.mp3`, "text": `Well, why don't we try some different ways of doing it?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6459.635_6464.719.mp3`, "text": `We could have the Radiohead computer voice do it.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6466.02_6468.341.mp3`, "text": `And the Stephen Hawking voice.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6468.421_6469.582.mp3`, "text": `Yeah.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6469.722_6472.945.mp3`, "text": `You could send it to me and I could do a dramatic reading of it.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6475.687_6476.808.mp3`, "text": `We could try and put it to music.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6477.468_6480.03.mp3`, "text": `I could sing it folk musician style.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6480.19_6480.35.mp3`, "text": `Yeah.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6480.51_6480.73.mp3`, "text": `Sure.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6480.81_6483.953.mp3`, "text": `We could try a lot of different ways of reading that disclaimer.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6484.742_6490.145.mp3`, "text": `The disclaimer that basically says that anytime you invest your money, you are at risk of losing it.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6490.225_6490.445.mp3`, "text": `Right.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6490.925_6492.266.mp3`, "text": `Yeah.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6494.467_6502.992.mp3`, "text": `You know, I imagine a lot of our listeners are sitting in the ten thousand square foot home in Palo Alto they just recently bought.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6505.113_6506.174.mp3`, "text": `They've never lived alone.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6507.655_6511.417.mp3`, "text": `And the first thing they bought was a hundred inch television.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6512.157_6518.547.mp3`, "text": `Which they mounted... Not above the fireplace, but in front of the fireplace because they never expect to use the fireplace.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6519.608_6522.991.mp3`, "text": `And they're sitting on a beanbag chair with their game controller in their hand.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6523.811_6529.976.mp3`, "text": `And next to them is a Filson bag with like two million dollars in... Or two million euros in it.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6531.357_6539.1.mp3`, "text": `And the only thing on the wall... is a giant poster of a white Lamborghini with a girl in a bathing suit sprawled on the hood.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6539.26_6539.66.mp3`, "text": `Right.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6540.381_6542.742.mp3`, "text": `And they're thinking to themselves, I've made it.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6543.182_6543.983.mp3`, "text": `I have all this money.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6544.023_6544.963.mp3`, "text": `I have this huge house.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6545.183_6546.224.mp3`, "text": `Now, what do I do?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6547.445_6549.866.mp3`, "text": `I've got this, I've got these euros in this Filson bag.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6551.547_6556.67.mp3`, "text": `I've got the best virtual reality headset that I could have.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6556.73_6558.371.mp3`, "text": `the tech guys at my company buy.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6559.641_6568.365.mp3`, "text": `build right but there's really not that much content for VR gaming yet and you know what do I do?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6568.665_6570.045.mp3`, "text": `what do I do and what?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6570.746_6590.278.mp3`, "text": `what we're offering them is the opportunity to take some of that money and invest it and get involved in the larger enterprise of of global capitalism by becoming investors owners And that's a great opportunity.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6590.758_6593.959.mp3`, "text": `And little by little, then they're going to build an art collection.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6594.639_6595.759.mp3`, "text": `They're going to buy some furniture.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6596.76_6599.461.mp3`, "text": `They might meet someone that they fall in love with.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6599.501_6605.182.mp3`, "text": `This could be the beginning of a much wider, broader life for them.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6606.483_6606.663.mp3`, "text": `Yeah.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6606.903_6615.124.mp3`, "text": `So, I mean, our typical listener is probably going to be... Well, either as I've just described.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6616.205_6622.35.mp3`, "text": `Or someone working on a collective farm somewhere in the Midwest as part of like a religious...` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6623.51_6629.935.mp3`, "text": `I'm not going to say cult, but like a religious organization that is into organic farming and they're all living collectively.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6629.995_6640.103.mp3`, "text": `And then at night they sit and listen to podcasts around a sort of central dining establishment where they're eating scrambled eggs.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_664.509_665.01.mp3`, "text": `No, no.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6641.554_6643.815.mp3`, "text": `at picnic tables in a giant hall.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6645.956_6650.478.mp3`, "text": `And that organization too could benefit from a little bit of wise investment.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_665.39_673.697.mp3`, "text": `I think we should let people watch it themselves and have their own experience of this idea.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6651.618_6668.326.mp3`, "text": `You know, I understand that you have to buy seed every year, but with the money that you have left over for buying seed and from, you know, and from hand spinning your simple garments, invest a little bit of that money and watch it grow.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6673.414_6673.875.mp3`, "text": `That's yeah.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6673.935_6677.977.mp3`, "text": `It feels like, you know, I'm just trying to picture our listeners.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6678.037_6678.477.mp3`, "text": `Yeah.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6679.238_6688.083.mp3`, "text": `I mean, I definitely see a lot of people, part of RV culture, Winnebago culture, RV, RV drivers.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6688.103_6688.403.mp3`, "text": `Yeah.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6689.184_6690.344.mp3`, "text": `We'll probably be listening to the show.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6690.424_6692.485.mp3`, "text": `Some, some, some frackers.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6695.067_6696.007.mp3`, "text": `Canadian frackers.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6696.027_6696.308.mp3`, "text": `Yeah.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6698.82_6699.221.mp3`, "text": `Who else?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6701.723_6705.225.mp3`, "text": `Polynesian South Pacific Islanders, of course, are going to be a big demographic for us.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6711.81_6718.275.mp3`, "text": `Obviously, NASA employees have been a big part of my career.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6719.096_6722.979.mp3`, "text": `And I can only presume they're going to follow us to this new podcast.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_673.717_675.659.mp3`, "text": `Because I think it's something that everybody...` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6765.071_6772.515.mp3`, "text": `Spiders, spiders, you know, cars, the movie or cars.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6777.838_6778.198.mp3`, "text": `I like it.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6778.398_6778.759.mp3`, "text": `I like it.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6782.727_6782.967.mp3`, "text": `Right?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6782.987_6785.468.mp3`, "text": `We could do a few shows on complacency.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6787.73_6788.67.mp3`, "text": `There's a lot to talk about.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_679.935_681.076.mp3`, "text": `It's a classic idea.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6792.732_6796.094.mp3`, "text": `Now you're throwing some shade on whether or not I'm introverted or not?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6796.134_6796.494.mp3`, "text": `Yeah.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6796.995_6797.335.mp3`, "text": `Okay.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6797.495_6797.795.mp3`, "text": `All right.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6802.909_6803.91.mp3`, "text": `Well, maybe, I guess.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6803.95_6804.77.mp3`, "text": `Yeah.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6804.79_6806.231.mp3`, "text": `We'll have to fight that out.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_681.677_681.857.mp3`, "text": `Right.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6816.737_6817.457.mp3`, "text": `No, no, of course not.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6817.477_6819.058.mp3`, "text": `You don't give it all away in the first episode.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6819.078_6819.238.mp3`, "text": `Right.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_682.378_686.341.mp3`, "text": `I think that the way you got onto that was that you were describing your process.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6820.088_6825.931.mp3`, "text": `I have a long list of people I'd like to thank, but I can save it for later.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6825.971_6837.296.mp3`, "text": `But I'm super grateful that people have made it all the way to this podcast and then all the way to the end of this podcast to hear this gratitude.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6839.016_6841.097.mp3`, "text": `Thank you, guys.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6843.098_6843.398.mp3`, "text": `All right.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6844.99_6845.831.mp3`, "text": `All right, I'll talk to you later.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6845.971_6849.535.mp3`, "text": `This is the most formal ending of a podcast I've ever heard.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6849.875_6850.256.mp3`, "text": `I know it is.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6850.276_6852.298.mp3`, "text": `It's just like, Dan, thank you so much.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6852.438_6853.379.mp3`, "text": `Great talking to you.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6853.439_6853.74.mp3`, "text": `Yeah.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6861.598_6863.58.mp3`, "text": `No, no, it's next to impossible.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6863.62_6871.989.mp3`, "text": `You have to either ring a bell, which is a signal that it's time for me to eat, or do this kind of like, great talking to you.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_6872.009_6875.412.mp3`, "text": `We're going to review your submission and we'll get back to you next week.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_689.424_689.625.mp3`, "text": `Right.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_693.051_698.296.mp3`, "text": `Incidentally, that's one of my superpowers to remember what we were talking about.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_699.397_705.902.mp3`, "text": `And I very seldom use it on my other podcast, but it actually is a superpower that I have access to.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_706.403_709.786.mp3`, "text": `I can pretty much always get back to the jumping off point.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_714.25_714.73.mp3`, "text": `Okay, good.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_722.237_723.438.mp3`, "text": `Right.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_723.498_731.666.mp3`, "text": `For those listeners who are not familiar with Back to Work, my impression of it is that it's an exceptionally successful productivity podcast.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_734.969_735.65.mp3`, "text": `Life hacking.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_739.053_739.233.mp3`, "text": `Right.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_739.313_739.733.mp3`, "text": `Guru.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_739.753_739.914.mp3`, "text": `Guru.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_763.508_766.87.mp3`, "text": `You guys were hacking like the the Mac Lisa thing.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_768.258_769.338.mp3`, "text": `And that's the Mac Lisa.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_770.159_773.659.mp3`, "text": `Trying to figure out like how to get, how to optimize your Lisa's.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_806.408_809.41.mp3`, "text": `Oh, I am his very much.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_809.51_810.47.mp3`, "text": `I am Merlin's pet.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_810.71_811.07.mp3`, "text": `Yes.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_844.252_845.592.mp3`, "text": `It was very fun.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_845.692_845.952.mp3`, "text": `Yeah.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_846.372_846.893.mp3`, "text": `It was very fun.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_846.913_852.334.mp3`, "text": `I was surprised that we were very different sizes.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_853.954_860.615.mp3`, "text": `It seemed like there was almost no item of your clothing that would have worked for me.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_860.715_861.475.mp3`, "text": `I'm not even sure.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_861.495_863.536.mp3`, "text": `I'm not even sure if I could wear your socks.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_863.616_863.916.mp3`, "text": `Maybe.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_866.616_868.957.mp3`, "text": `Well, you know, I keep shrinking.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_870.16_874.323.mp3`, "text": `Because my spine is compressing from all the impacts.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_875.604_878.906.mp3`, "text": `You know, all the times I've had to jump off of a low retaining wall.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_879.787_882.088.mp3`, "text": `And little by little, I've lost about an inch.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_883.109_884.67.mp3`, "text": `Yeah, it's not so good.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_884.69_886.652.mp3`, "text": `Oof.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_891.913_895.876.mp3`, "text": `I was six three and some change at one point.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_896.016_896.316.mp3`, "text": `Okay.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_899.018_900.539.mp3`, "text": `You are for a long time.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_900.899_903.101.mp3`, "text": `I was six three and some change.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_903.301_911.427.mp3`, "text": `And now the last time I was at, and then, so I went to a doctor at one point and they measured me and said that I was six.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_912.347_913.048.mp3`, "text": `What did they say?` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_913.148_915.069.mp3`, "text": `Something like six one and some change.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_915.109_919.152.mp3`, "text": `And I was like, your instruments are not calibrated.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_920.693_923.654.mp3`, "text": `And, you know, and they're like a medical office.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_923.674_924.594.mp3`, "text": `They just scoff.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_926.114_932.336.mp3`, "text": `But then I went to a doctor more recently and they said I was six, two and some change, six, two and a half.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_933.376_934.157.mp3`, "text": `And I was.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_940.92_949.026.mp3`, "text": `But, I mean, I was upset, but, you know, six one and three quarters, that was just unacceptable.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_949.046_955.891.mp3`, "text": `I cannot possibly have lost two inches of height, no matter how many retaining walls I've jumped off of.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_957.292_974.824.mp3`, "text": `And so, six two and some, you know, six two and a half, I was like, it's... It's the old thing where I'd already had a traumatic experience of being measured improperly, and now I was being given back some of that lost height, and I was like, okay, fine, I'll take it.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_975.785_976.866.mp3`, "text": `I don't know.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_977.426_985.185.mp3`, "text": `I've done a lot of walking, and maybe... All the padding in the bottom of my foot has been compressed or something.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_987.287_990.929.mp3`, "text": `Or maybe I lost an inch in my ankles or something.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_990.99_993.692.mp3`, "text": `I'm just not sure where I could have lost an inch.` },
    { "file": `roadwork_001_997.434_1000.356.mp3`, "text": `A little bit of swelling in my scalp probably went down.` },]